# Vouched contributors for Sideload Spanish.
#
# Only vouched users can open PRs and issues.
# Maintainers can vouch for new contributors by commenting "vouch" on an issue.
# Denounced users are auto-closed.
#
# Format: one handle per line (without @), sorted alphabetically.
# Prefix with - to denounce. Optionally add platform: github:username.
# Details can follow a space after the handle.

github:nycterent
